{"tid":1823912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以豬肉代替獎學金，曾家過年氣氛","createTime":"2020-01-14T05:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T05:50:21.000Z","uid":184099,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0425cd64306a6aac77fae2a89bae6d72bb262e54","tid":1823912,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vYstWRe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvYstWRe.jpg&h=4b4459d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1月8日，王昊通知班主任統計班上前三名的同學，老師們這才知道今年的獎勵是豬肉。由於那裡沒有300至400斤的生豬，王昊到六盤水生豬市場購買。最後，以 19.6元每斤的價格買了7頭豬，每頭豬平均400多斤，總共3000多斤，折合價值5萬餘元。<br />\n<br />\n 9日，在學校的表彰大會上，豬肉依次排開，學生根據名次領到自己的豬肉，第一名30斤，第二名20斤，第三名一隻豬腳。一些同學將豬肉用竹竿 抬回家，低年級的同學則是家長用背篼背回家，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">引來旁人羨慕的目光。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.online.sh.cn/edu/content/2020-01/13/content_9482562_2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.online.sh.cn%2Fedu%2Fcontent%2F2020-01%2F13%2Fcontent_9482562_2.htm&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=47fd2e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.online.sh.cn/edu/content/2020-01/13/content_9482562_2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有肉兒吃，油滋滋，美滋滋，真香。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n黨兒，愛你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8a6b7617008ec054febac09808501cd79c965d","tid":1823912,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"最後，以 19.6元每斤的價格買了7頭豬，每頭豬平均400多斤，總共3000多斤，折合價值5萬餘元。<br />\n<br />\n派完剩底嗰啲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"h